flowchart TD
    SetupStart([Open setup]) --> ProfileInput[Enter profile and request registration options]
    ProfileInput --> ProfileValid{Profile and account valid?}
    ProfileValid -- No --> SetupError[Show safe setup error]
    ProfileValid -- Yes --> RegisterPrompt[Run platform passkey prompt]
    RegisterPrompt --> AttestationValid{Attestation valid?}
    AttestationValid -- No --> SetupRetry[Clear ceremony and offer retry]
    AttestationValid -- Yes --> PersistInitial[Store active public credential]
    PersistInitial --> IssueRecoveryCode[Store digest and return code once]
    IssueRecoveryCode --> AcknowledgeCode[Copy or download and acknowledge]
    AcknowledgeCode --> PasskeySetupComplete([Setup complete])

    AuthStart([Open sign in]) --> UsernameInput[Enter username]
    UsernameInput --> AuthOptions[Request authentication options]
    AuthOptions --> AuthPrompt[Run passkey assertion prompt]
    AuthPrompt --> AssertionValid{Active credential and assertion valid?}
    AssertionValid -- No --> AuthFailure[Generic failure with retry or recovery]
    AssertionValid -- Yes --> UpdateCredentialUse[Consume challenge and update credential use]
    UpdateCredentialUse --> IssueSession[Issue Application Session]
    IssueSession --> Authenticated([Signed in])
